title: Ground News - Titusville Man Sentenced to 11 Years in Prison After Fatal Hit-and-Run Crash in Cocoa
text:
Summary by Space Coast Daily Jacquiece Witcher, 38, sentenced to 11 years in prisonA 38-year-old Titusville man will spend the next 11 years in prison for leaving the scene of a deadly crash. BREVARD COUNTY •. COCOA, FLORIDA – A 38-year-old Titusville man will spend the next 11 years in prison for leaving the scene of a deadly crash. Police say Jacquiece Witcher, 38, entered a guilty plea for the 2019 hit and run crash which killed 61-year-old Bruce Calkins of Rockledge. W… Share menu More
